{"tid":1024299,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"今次我寫左var比大家用","createTime":"2019-02-16T12:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T06:57:35.000Z","uid":235009,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58ef422cd18aaad858fcf50e0e39baf89a5ec25e","tid":1024299,"uid":235009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"我係呢個post既樓主<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1008316/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1008316/page/1</a><br />\n今次加左個新功能計Value at Risk<br />\n<br />\n應該好多人都知咩係Var 我唔多解釋係咩黎<br />\n計係簡單 但係拎data好麻煩<br />\n希望呢個功能可以比大家好快計到自己既portfolio既var<br />\n我整左兩個var計法 一個係用返過去歷史黎計 一個用normal distribution<br />\n<br />\n上次經驗係好多人都唔識點用個網<br />\n其實我都覺啲form整得唔好<br />\n但係我front end無咩心機學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以只係用default就算<br />\n以後多啲時間先再執個form<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nStock list: <a href=\"http://如果你想計0001.HK同0002.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%BD%A0%E6%83%B3%E8%A8%880001.HK%E5%90%8C0002.HK&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L6F0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=13e19c9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">如果你想計0001.HK同0002.HK</a> 打 '1 2' 用space bar隔開兩個數字<br />\nWeighting list: 如果你既組合係 {<a href=\"http://0001.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0001.HK&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L6F0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=cb006b20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0001.HK</a>: 10萬, <a href=\"http://0002.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0002.HK&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L6F0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=71556f37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0002.HK</a>: 8萬} 打 '100000 80000' 或者 '0.56 0.44' <br />\nN days: 如果你想計1 day return 既Var就打1<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkportfolioanalysis.com/analysis/value_at_risk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkportfolioanalysis.com%2Fanalysis%2Fvalue_at_risk%2F&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L6F0%2BEj